<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="367" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,764,646,911]" pageId="8" pageNumber="367">
<collectingCounty box="[189,241,646,672]" pageId="8" pageNumber="367">This</collectingCounty>
species was previously recorded from 
<collectingMunicipality pageId="8" pageNumber="367">Liberian</collectingMunicipality>
<collectingRegion box="[241,321,680,706]" country="Liberia" name="Nimba" pageId="8" pageNumber="367">Nimba</collectingRegion>
(Verschuren, 1977; Wolton 
<emphasis box="[688,749,680,706]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="367">et al</emphasis>
., 1982). 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03BD87F43F796D4CFECCFDD9FE33FC4E:8ECB60393F796D4CFF01FD52FE82FD25" box="[239,322,714,740]" county="This" municipality="Liberian" name="During" pageId="8" pageNumber="367" stateProvince="Nimba">During</location>
this survey, it was recorded widely in forested habitats between 400 and 
<elevation box="[601,764,748,774]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="367" unit="m" value="1000.0">
<quantity box="[601,700,748,774]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="367" unit="m" value="1000.0">1,000 m</quantity>
a.s.l.
</elevation>
on the Liberian side. This species was distinguished from the similar 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Aellen" authorityYear="1959" box="[368,536,817,843]" class="Mammalia" family="Nycteridae" genus="Nycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="367" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="intermedia">
<emphasis box="[368,536,817,843]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="367">N. intermedia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by its larger size (forearm length 
<quantity box="[352,531,851,877]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.43" metricValueMax="4.88" metricValueMin="3.9799999999999995" pageId="8" pageNumber="367" unit="mm" value="44.3" valueMax="48.8" valueMin="39.8">39.8–48.8 mm</quantity>
, and greatest skull length 
<quantity box="[233,407,885,911]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.9899999999999998" metricValueMax="2.01" metricValueMin="1.97" pageId="8" pageNumber="367" unit="mm" value="19.9" valueMax="20.1" valueMin="19.7">19.7–20.1 mm</quantity>
, 
<emphasis box="[419,434,885,911]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="367">n</emphasis>
= 5).
</paragraph>
